\itemize{
\item \strong{Deposit Monitoring}: Check \code{is_deposit_enabled} and \code{deposit_min_size} before initiating deposits.
\item \strong{Withdrawal Validation}: Verify \code{is_withdraw_enabled}, \code{withdrawal_min_size}, \code{withdrawal_min_fee},
and \code{withdraw_precision} before submitting withdrawals.
\item \strong{Chain Selection}: Compare fees and confirmation times across chains to optimise transfers.
