Get All Symbols

Retrieves metadata for all trading pairs, optionally filtered by market
segment. Returns the same fields as \code{get_symbol()} for every pair.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: GET with optional \code{market} query parameter.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Converts array of symbol objects to \code{data.table} rows.
}
}

