\subsection{Method \code{get_trade_history()}}{
Get Trade History

Retrieves the most recent 100 trades for a symbol. Each trade includes
the price, size, side (buy/sell), and nanosecond-precision timestamp.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Request}: GET with \code{symbol} query parameter.
\item \strong{Parsing}: Converts array of trade objects to \code{data.table}.
\item \strong{Timestamp Conversion}: Coerces \code{time} (nanoseconds) to POSIXct in-place.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/market/histories}
